{"tid":1593032,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"比特幣價格最多挫15% 跌穿8000美元","createTime":"2019-09-25T01:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T01:36:57.000Z","uid":31907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"390769f664ac8d5933aeb1087de4f992ee261482","tid":1593032,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T01:36:38.000Z","msg":"比特幣價格最多挫15% 跌穿8000美元 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019-9-25 08:09海外新聞<br />\n&lt;匯港通訊&gt;   CoinDesk 數據顯示,比特幣價格最多下跌15%至7944.33美元,是6月中,即4個月以來首度跌穿8000美元。<br />\n<br />\n分析員指出,比特幣滑落是受到一系列因素影響,包括跌穿9000美元重要技術支持位、紐約證交所將推出比特幣期貨產品、比特幣礦商突然減少開採量等。<br />\n<br />\n其他虛擬貨幣價格跌幅最多也達20%"},{"pid":"614555799171359d3bc5cb1b4d7e8efe07dc4763","tid":1593032,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T01:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"}]}